OL,3,CFertility unit's licence suspended
OL,4,Cafter 'errors' in freezing process
OL,6,FA fertility clinic has had its licence
OL,7,Fsuspended after admitting "errors" in
OL,8,Fits freezing processes led to some
OL,9,Fembryos "either not surviving or being
OL,10,Fundetectable".
OL,12,FHomerton Fertility Centre in east
OL,13,FLondon said it had increased security
OL,14,Fand made staff "work in pairs" after
OL,15,Fthree separate incidents in the last
OL,16,Fyear within the unit.
OL,18,FThe Telegraph reported that the centre
OL,19,Fhad been reported to police over fears
OL,20,Fembryos were being destroyed.
