OL,3,CFertility unit's licence suspended
OL,4,Cafter 'errors' in freezing process
OL,6,FThe Human Fertilisation and Embryology
OL,7,FAuthority (HFEA) said it had suspended
OL,8,Fthe centre's licence because of
OL,9,F"significant concerns" about the
OL,10,Fclinic and a "potential risk to
OL,11,Fpatients, gametes and embryos".
OL,13,FThe suspension means the unit will not
OL,14,Fbe able to accept any new bookings for
OL,15,Ftreatment but existing patients can
OL,16,Fstill access its services.
