OL,3,CFertility unit's licence suspended
OL,4,Cafter 'errors' in freezing process
OL,6,FThe Metropolitan Police said officers
OL,7,Fwent to the centre on Friday "after
OL,8,Fconcerns were raised by the Homerton
OL,9,FHealthcare NHS Foundation Trust",
OL,10,Fadding that there is no police
OL,11,Finvestigation at this time".
OL,13,FIn a letter apologising to patients,
OL,14,Fthe chief executive of Homerton
OL,15,FHealthcare NHS Foundation Trust,
OL,16,FLouise Ashley, said the centre had "re-
OL,17,Fchecked all competencies of staff
OL,18,Fwithin the unit".
