OL,6,FShe added: "We have now had three
OL,7,Fseparate incidents in the last year
OL,8,Fwithin the unit, which have
OL,9,Fhighlighted errors in a small number
OL,10,Fof our freezing processes.
OL,12,F"Tragically this has, in some cases,
OL,13,Fresulted in a small number of embryos
OL,14,Feither not surviving or being
OL,15,Fundetectable.
