OL,6,F"We have external clinical experts
OL,7,Finvestigating these incidents and,
OL,8,Fwhilst they have not been able to find
OL,9,Fany direct cause to explain this, we
OL,10,Fhave made changes in the unit to
OL,11,Fprevent reoccurrence of such
OL,12,Fincidents."
OL,14,FMs Ashley said the HFEA had suspended
OL,15,Fthe clinic's licence until May 2024.
OL,17,FPeter Thompson, chief executive of the
OL,18,FHFEA, said: "The HFEA has suspended
OL,19,FHomerton Fertility Centre's licence to
OL,20,Foperate with immediate effect, due to
OL,21,Fsignificant concerns about the clinic.
