OL,6,F"The HFEA licence committee made this
OL,7,Fdecision because of the potential risk
OL,8,Fto patients, gametes and embryos if
OL,9,Fthe clinic's licence is not suspended
OL,10,Fwith immediate effect.
OL,12,F"We appreciate this may cause concern
OL,13,Fto patients who are undergoing
OL,14,Ftreatment at the clinic, or have eggs,
OL,15,Fsperm and/or embryos stored there.
